      <title>美国希望没收与前刚果领导人有关的纽约豪华公寓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/us-seeks-forfeiture-of-luxury-apartment-in-trump-hotel-and-tower</link>
